HEADWORD: Interadditive
<hw>In`ter*ad"di*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Added or
placed between the parts of another thing, as a clause inserted
parenthetically in a sentence.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

